casebody.data:
A.B.A., Plaintiff-Movant,
v.
T.A., Defendant-Respondent. M-19 September Term 2018
080784 Supreme Court of New Jersey. September 12, 2018

ORDER

It is ORDERED that the motion for counsel fees and costs is granted. Counsel fees are awarded in the amount of $6,127.50, and costs are awarded in the amount of $82.20 for a total award of $6,209.70.
